headline: Dell Technologies Stock Gets Price Target Boost from Top Analyst
summary: Dell Technologies (DELL) is back in the spotlight as a leading Wall Street firm raises its price target on the stock, citing continued strength in the company’s AI-driven growth and enterprise demand. Notably, five-star-rated analyst Simon Leopold from Raymond James lifted his price target on Dell stock from $139 to $144, while keeping his Buy rating.
